data.description: Nestled on a spacious corner lot, this charming 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home boasts a design that marries comfort with ease. The heart of this residence is a large open floor plan, perfect for entertaining and gatherings, leading out to a covered patio for serene outdoor living. The expansive master suite is a retreat of its own with a luxurious-sized bathroom and a generous walk-in closet. An additional office/media room provides a versatile space for work or relaxation. Wide hallways enhance the open feel, and the convenience of a 2-car garage adds to the home's practical appeal. This property is a harmonious blend of style and functionality, creating the perfect setting for a comfortable lifestyle.
